laimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.017402, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn89053204, 1923-11-13, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/gu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["sumter", "georgia", "sumter county (ga.)", "sumter county", "newspapers", "united states", "americus (ga.)", "americus"], "subject_headings": ["Americus (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Sumter County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Georgia--Americus", "Georgia--Sumter County", "United States--Georgia--Sumter--Americus"], "subjects": [{"americus": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:americus&fo=json"}, {"americus (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:americus+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"georgia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:georgia&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"sumter": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:sumter&fo=json"}, {"sumter county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:sumter+county&fo=json"}, {"sumter county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:sumter+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T20:59:43.868Z", "title": "Americus times-recorder (Americus, Ga.;[Americus, Ga.?]), November 13, 1923", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053204/1923-11-13/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053204/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89053204"], "batch": ["gu_ara_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1891", "description": ["Weekly, <Dec. 26, 2014-> Vol. 1, no. 13 (Apr. 19, 1891)- Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online c